updateManifest.description: The Google Assistant for KaiOS allows you to quickly access your Google Assistant from the main menu. Check if you need to take an umbrella when you leave home, make calls hands free during your commute, and unwind by playing your favorite tunes. You personal Google is here to help. Ask questions and get things done. Use it anytime, anywhere.
